With the new aaxp and tone of PoP I bet it will rely more on magicians speciality of dealing with summoned creatures.  Turn summoned may become useful.  Pets can be given swords of runes for more procage.  The anti summon dd line may get a boost.  The pet swarm and suspend options will increase pet viability in different situations.<br>
